Program: Great Lives
Title: Johnny Weissmuller
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00glw8t
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 9 May 2006
Presented by Matthew Parris, athlete Duncan Goodhew nominates the athlete-turned-actor Johnny Weissmuller, and his only son, Johnny Jr, joins them to discuss his father's childhood, swimming talent and Hollywood adventures.